        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Small businesses scaling past 10-15 people.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " This is when tribal knowledge starts breaking down. The founder cannot answer every question anymore. Trainual captures what is in everyone's head before it walks out the door.",
