        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Trainual is purpose-built for SOPs, onboarding, and training—areas where Google Docs and Notion lack structure. It adds role-based assignments, completion tracking, quizzes, and automated reminders. Many teams keep Notion for general notes but centralize all process documentation in Trainual.",
