        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Most small teams can get a basic playbook running in one to two days. Set up your org structure in an hour, document your five most critical processes, invite your team, and start assigning. You do not need to document everything upfront—Trainual is designed for incremental, ongoing improvement.",
